title: The Week India - 25 September 2016 (gnv64)

The Week India - 25 September 2016
English | 116 pages | True PDF | 27.5 mb

The Week is the best selling general interest English news magazine. The magazine covers politics, entertainment, social issues, trends, technology, lifestyle, who's hot, who's not, and everything else you should be knowing. 
In this issue: Cauvery row engulfs two major states. Are water tribunals ineffective? Is the BCCI getting cornered in the ICC? Northeastern cuisine makes a quiet entry in Delhi's fine-dining scene
